title: Euro 2016 Qualifier Highlights - 2015.06.14 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Euro 2016 Qualifier Highlights
On: itv HD 
Date: Sunday 14th June 2015 
Time: 22:50 to 00:15 

Matt Smith presents a comprehensive round-up of all the weekend's Euro Qualifiers. Group E leaders England travel to Slovenia to try and maintain their 100 percent record, while Wales take on Belgium at home in a top of the table clash. Scotland and Republic of Ireland go head-to-head in a game they must both win to keep in contention in Group D. In Group F, Northern Ireland host group leaders Romania, who are just one point ahead of them.
